{"id":205878,"name":null,"username":"xesf","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/xesf/{size}/122_2.png","created_at":"2004-12-31T11:33:15.000Z","cooked":"<p>Changing Twinsens bodies isnt the best option because his animations. We dont have access yet on Viewer with animation edit option so we cant fixed the Twinsen animation with Zo body for example. The better you could do is to find an bodie similar to Twinsens one and replace it, probably the animations will be better showing.</p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":7,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:11:51.450Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":10.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7914,"topic_slug":"animation","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":1285,"username":"Blafards61","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/blafards61/{size}/32_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Changing Twinsen's bodies isn't the best option because his animations. We don't have access yet on Viewer with animation edit option so we can't fixed the Twinsen animation with Zo body for example. The better you could do is to find an bodie similar to Twinsens one and replace it, probably the animations will be better showing.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"group_moderator":true,"user_id":463,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/animation/79